ian Universities\u201d, Editura LIMES, Cluj-Napoca, 2007, {{ISBN|978-973-726-278-3}}, http://www.history-cluj.ro/Istorie/cercet/Nastasa/SuveraniiUniversitatilorI.pdf\n* Opri\u0219, Ioan: \u201cComisiunea Monumentelor Istorice / The Commission of Historic Monuments\u201d, Editura Enciclopedica, Bucuresti, 1994, {{ISBN|978-973-4500772}}\n* Opri\u015f, Ioan: \u201cAlexandru Lapedatu \u00een cultura rom\u00e2neasc\u0103 / Alexandru Lapedatu in the Romanian Culture\u201d, Editura Stiintifica, Bucuresti, 1996, {{ISBN|973-44-0190-4}}. Internet version edited by the Civic Academy Foundation, 2017 http://www.memorialsighet.ro/carti/alexandru-lapedatu-cultura-romaneasca/\n* Opri\u0219, Ioan: \u201cAlexandru Lapedatu \u015fi contemporanii s\u0103i / Alexandru Lapedatu and His Contemporaries\u201d, Editura Albastr\u0103, Cluj-Napoca 1997, {{ISBN|973-9215-46-7}}. Internet version edited by the Civic Academy Foundation, 2016 http://www.memorialsighet.ro/carti/alexandru-lapedatu-si-contemporanii-sai/\n* Opri\u015f, Ioan: \u201cGemenii Lapedatu. Istorie \u0219i finan\u021be / The Lapedatu Twins. History and Finances\u201d, Ed. Oscar Print, Bucharest, 2017, {{ISBN|978-9736-68435-7}}\n* Otiman, P\u0103un Ion: \u201c1948 \u2013 anul imensei jertfe a Academiei Romane / 1948 \u2013 the year of the tremendous sacrifice of the Romanian Academy\u201d, AKADEMOS ISTORIE, Nr. 4 (31), 2013, pp.&nbsp;115\u2013124. https://www.scribd.com/document/345599425/1948-anul-imensei-jertfe-a-Academiei-romane-pdf\n* Pop, Ioan-Aurel: \u201cAlexandru Lapedatu \u2013 un universitar clujean / Alexandru Lapedatu : A University Profesor in Cluj\u201d, ACADEMICA Annul XXVI, Nr. 9, September 2016, pp.&nbsp;5\u20138, http://www.acad.ro/academica2002/rev2016/pag_acad2016_nr311_sep.htm\n* Preda, Dr. G.: \u201c\u2018Activitatea \u2018Astrei\u2019 \u00een 25 de ani de la Unire (1918-1943) / Astra\u2019 Activity in the 25 Years since the Union (1918-1943)\u201d, Sibiu, 1944, Editura ASTREI, http://centrulslavici.uvvg.r