mine Polito\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Kill the Messenger (2014 film)|Kill the Messenger]]''\n| [[Gary Webb]]\n| Also producer\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Mission: Impossible&nbsp;\u2013 Rogue Nation]]''\n| William Brandt\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n|''[[Avengers: Age of Ultron]]''\n| Clint Barton / Hawkeye\n|\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Captain America: Civil War]]''\n| Clint Barton / Hawkeye\n|\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Arrival (film)|Arrival]]''\n| Ian Donnelly\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Wind River (film)|Wind River]]''\n| Cory Lambert\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The House (2017 film)|The House]]''\n| Tommy Papouli\n| Cameo\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Tag (2018 film)|Tag]]''\n| Jerry Pierce\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Avengers: Endgame]]''\n| Clint Barton / Hawkeye\n| \n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Arctic Dogs]]''\n| Swifty\n| Voice role\n|}\n<!--Do not put films that have not begun filming yet per WP:CRYSTAL-->\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1995\n| ''[[Deadly Games]]''\n| Tod\n| Episode: \"Boss\"\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Strange Luck]]''\n| Jojo Picard\n| Episode: \"Blinded by the Son\"\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[A Friend's Betrayal]]''\n| Simon\n| [[Television film|TV film]]\n|-\n| 1997\n| ''A Nightmare Come True''\n| Steven Zarn\n| TV film\n|-\n| 1998\n| ''[[To Have & to Hold (TV series)|To Have & to Hold]]''\n| Ted Fury\n| Uncredited{{citation needed|date=August 2019}}; episode: \"Tangled Up in You\"\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[The Net (U.S. TV series)|The Net]]''\n| Ted Nida\n| Episode: \"Chem Lab\"\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[Time of Your Life (U.S. TV series)|Time of Your Life]]''\n| Taylor\n| Episode: \"The Time the Truth Was Told\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Angel (1999 TV series)|Angel]]''\n| Penn\n| Episode: \"[[Somnambulist (Angel)|Somnambulist]]\"\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]''\n| Roger Jennings\n| Episode: \"[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation (season 2)#ep29|Alter Boys]]\"\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[The It Factor]]''\n| Himself\n| Reality television series\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[House (TV series)|